latestPosts.caption:
Began March by getting featured under “brands to look out for in 2024”, 3 out of our 5 products turned out to be best sellers on Nykaa and nearly recording the month with the highest sales till now🧿🤞

Living between 2 countries while being a mom to a brand is nothing but a full of “guilt” journey, whenever I am in Dubai I feel like a part of me is back in Bombay with my girls even though I am working full time from Dubai it still doesn’t feel the same as it does being present in the office looking after a 1-year-old 🥺 

That’s when I started celebrating the little milestones of TSDC like any other mom does, manifesting became a big part of my journey, “act as if you’re already there” they said & IT WORKED. As soon as I started manifesting energies I saw a shift in not only myself but all external forces including my brand performance in numbers & concerning awareness, all the delays happening with the new production started becoming clearer while only leading to creating a perfect product. 

As we stand in the third month of March, I promise by December we will know why we got featured on this list🧿🙏🏼

latestPosts.caption:
This weekend’s highlight was mumma papa visiting us🫶🏻✨😘 They made your childhood magical. Now it’s your turn to make their life fulfilling 🫶🏻

As a child, my favorite part of every college break was going home to be fed, pampered, and taken around by my parents like a little tourist in my own hometown. Those memories are etched in joy.

Now, years later, it’s my turn.
They visit me, and I find myself wanting to do it all for them , book the experiences, take them to new cafés, walk them through the city I now call home, and just watch them soak it all in.

From being the kid tugging on their hand to now holding theirs and saying “come, I want to show you something” life really does come full circle.

Time spent with parents hits differently as you grow older. It’s not just quality time it’s gratitude, nostalgia, and pride all wrapped into one.

Here’s to carving out time, making new memories, and giving them the same joy they once gave us, effortlessly.

latestPosts.caption:
When I started The Skin Diet Company, it was rooted in one belief — that your skin deserves the best of superfoods🫶🏻

Last year, we entered a new era with our Barrier Beauty range — starting with our Lip Barrier Oil, followed by your favorite Lip Barrier Tints. The love you showed made it clear: the future is barrier-first.🤍

And now, after nearly a year of meticulous formulation, I’m so proud to introduce our Lip Barrier Butter 🍒 ☕️ 🧁🧈 — powered with ceramides & peptides to repair, nourish and protect like never before.

This launch is where precision meets beauty.
Where repair means repair

Let’s butter up and build that barrier 🧈
